    <item>
      <title>印度政府在抗议声中推进电力私有化</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-13/indian-state-proceeds-with-power-privatization-amid-protests</link>
      <description><![CDATA[印度人口最多的北方邦正在推进一项备受争议的计划，将部分电力设施私有化，以确保在电力需求不断增长的情况下实现可靠​​的供电。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-13/indian-state-proceeds-with-power-privatization-amid-protests</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 13 Jan 2025 10:27:08 GMT</pubDate>
