    <item>
      <title>摩根士丹利的威尔逊认为美元走强将导致利润出现巨大差距</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-13/morgan-stanley-s-wilson-sees-big-gap-in-profits-on-strong-dollar</link>
      <description><![CDATA[摩根士丹利策略师表示，美元上涨可能会导致本季度美国企业的盈利情况出现巨大差距，国内业务型企业的表现将超过国际收入较大的企业。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-13/morgan-stanley-s-wilson-sees-big-gap-in-profits-on-strong-dollar</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 13 Jan 2025 10:06:26 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>印度银行寻求十多年来首笔美元贷款</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-13/bank-of-india-seeks-its-first-dollar-loan-in-more-than-a-decade</link>
      <description><![CDATA[印度银行表示，该行正在营销自 2012 年以来的首笔美元银团贷款，金额高达 4 亿美元。此时，越来越多的印度借款人正在利用全球信贷市场。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-13/bank-of-india-seeks-its-first-dollar-loan-in-more-than-a-decade</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 13 Jan 2025 08:25:12 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>印度资产遭受重创，卢比跌破 86 创下新低</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-13/rupee-falls-past-86-to-new-record-on-dollar-rally-oil-surge</link>
      <description><![CDATA[由于美元走强和油价上涨，人们更加担心印度这个全球增长最快的主要经济体之一将陷入经济放缓，印度资产遭到抛售，导致卢比出现近两年来最大跌幅。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-13/rupee-falls-past-86-to-new-record-on-dollar-rally-oil-surge</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 13 Jan 2025 04:57:36 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>由于美国对俄罗斯的制裁威胁供应，油价创下五个月新高</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-12/latest-oil-market-news-and-analysis-for-jan-13</link>
      <description><![CDATA[由于美国对俄罗斯能源行业实施新一轮制裁，威胁到全球最大产油国之一的石油供应，油价上涨至五个月来的最高水平。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-12/latest-oil-market-news-and-analysis-for-jan-13</guid>
      <pubDate>Sun, 12 Jan 2025 23:02:46 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
